{"lemma":"حَرَجاتٌ","slug":"حَرَجاتٌ","root":"ح.ر.ج","root_slug":"ح-ر-ج","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ر-ج","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حَرَج","root":"حرج","pos":"N","occurrence_count":15},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7562","n7566","n7567","n7568","n7569"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be in a critical situation"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be forbidden"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to commit a sin, an offense"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to embarrass, to hinder"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to prohibit"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tightness, difficulty, critical situation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"constraint, limitation, restriction","examples":[{"text":"بِلَا حَرَجٍ","english":"unhesitatingly (lit. without restriction)"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"tight, close; impenetrable due to denseness of trees or other things"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"woodlands, woods, forestland","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"المنبت والزراعة الغلطارية المسطّحة موطنها أمريكا الشمالية، وتوجد في الأحراج والمناطق الجبلية المكشوفة.","english":"The place where the checkerberry grows and is planted is Northern America where it is native, and it is found in woodlands and exposed mountainous regions."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"herds of camels","tags":["collective","obsolete"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew חרג (ħarág, “deviate”)."},"ipa":["/ħa.ri.d͡ʒa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7562","headword_ar":"حَرِجَ","root":"Hrj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a number of things)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became collected together:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and, necessarily,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became close, strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so accord. to an explanation of the inf. n. by Er-Rághib, in the TA:) said of anything,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, close, strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) One says of dust,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija A_ilaY HaAy^iTK","text_ar":"حَرِجَ اـِلَى حَايِطٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanadK","text_ar":"سَنَدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It rose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Az, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a narrow place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and became collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against a wall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an acclivity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth, Az, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija Sadoruhu","text_ar":"حَرِجَ صَدْرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His bosom became strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh, Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not expanded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dilated, by reason of what was good."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija","text_ar":"حَرِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone, aor. and inf. n. as above, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became disquieted, and contracted in bosom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became in doubt; he doubted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because doubt disquiets the mind. (So accord. to explanations of the inf. n. by Er-Rághib, in the TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija","text_ar":"حَرِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, [(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became straitened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in difficulty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the commission of a sin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crime:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below:) and hence, simply,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he committed a sin, a crime,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an act of disobedience for which he deserved punishment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looked, and was unable to move from his place by reason of fear and rage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harijati AlEayonu","text_ar":"حَرِجَتِ العَيْنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n. as above, (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eye became dazzled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaArat","text_ar":"حَارَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sank in its socket,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaArat","text_ar":"غَارَت"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and its vision became straitened:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it did not turn about,"},{"kind":"text","text":"nor"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wink, by reason of intent gazing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  Also, (S, A, K,) aor. as above, (K,) and so the inf. n., (S, K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, forbidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prohibited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attended with straitness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija EalaY~a Zulomuka","text_ar":"حَرِجَ عَلَىَّ ظُلْمُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wronging of thee is forbidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prohibited, to me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija Ealayohi Als~aHuwru","text_ar":"حَرِجَ عَلَيْهِ السَّحُورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The meal termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sHwr","text_ar":"سحور"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became forbidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prohibited, to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA,) namely, a man fasting,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and attended with difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of the straitness of the time thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harijati AlS~alaApu","text_ar":"حَرِجَتِ الصَّلَاةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prayer became forbidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prohibited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, and TA as from the K, [but not found by me in the copies of the K,])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalayohaA","text_ar":"عَلَيْهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to her"},{"kind":"text","text":"[by reason of legal impurity, as is shown in the A]. (A, TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija A_ilayohi","text_ar":"حَرِجَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He betook himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had recourse, to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, for protection from a strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija","text_ar":"حَرِجَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY ka*aA wa ka*aA","text_ar":"اـِلَى كَذَا وَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He betook himself to such and such things."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","Az","TA","S","A","K"]},{"entry_id":"n7566","headword_ar":"حُرْجٌ","root":"Hrj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."},{"kind":"page_break","n":543}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7567","headword_ar":"حِرْجٌ","root":"Hrj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The dog's portion of the prey,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"game;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K;) such as the head and the shanks and the belly: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is thrown to the dog, of the prey,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"game, that he has taken:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of flesh:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoraAjN","text_ar":"اَحْرَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cowry;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wadaEapN","text_ar":"وَدَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, A, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoraAjN","text_ar":"اَحْرَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHorijapN","text_ar":"اَحْرِجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiraAjN","text_ar":"حِرَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) the second, [as also the first,] a pl. of pauc.: (T, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cowries"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wadaEN","text_ar":"وَدَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which are hung upon the necks of dogs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A dog's collar"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of cowries"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a collar"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of cowries"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for any animal."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Az","S","A","K","T"]},{"entry_id":"n7568","headword_ar":"حَرَجٌ","root":"Hrj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of 1, q. v.:] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Straitness; a strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * TA.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sin, a crime,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an act of disobedience for which one deserves punishment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ivomN","text_ar":"اـِثْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, * K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HirojN","text_ar":"حِرْجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Yoo, S, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straitness"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is the consequence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sin"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crime."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh.) ―         -b3-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA Haraja","text_ar":"لَا حَرَجَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA baA^sa","text_ar":"لَا بَاسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will be, no harm"},{"kind":"text","text":"in thy doing this or that]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A_ivoma","text_ar":"لَا اـِثْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will be, no sin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crime"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAth, TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarijN","text_ar":"حَرِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in six places. ―         -b2-  Also, applied to a she-camel, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lean, lank, light of flesh, slender,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lank in the belly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurojuwjN","text_ar":"حُرْجُوجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) accord. to AZ, (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaruwjN","text_ar":"حَرُوجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurojuwjN","text_ar":"حُرْجُوجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"signifies, so applied, lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and sharp-spirited:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or this last, (K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaruwjN","text_ar":"حَرُوجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"largebodied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and long"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long upon the face of the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as distinguished from tall]: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also, (K,) or, as some say, and so do ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurojuwjN","text_ar":"حُرْجُوجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurojujN","text_ar":"حُرْجُجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juroHN","text_ar":"جُرْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) so applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long upon the face of the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) and some allow ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HirojiyjN","text_ar":"حِرْجِيجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurojuwjN","text_ar":"حُرْجُوجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) which last is originally ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurojujN","text_ar":"حُرْجُجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is originally ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juroHN","text_ar":"جُرْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HurojuwjN","text_ar":"حُرْجُوجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) and of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HirojiyjN","text_ar":"حِرْجِيجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAjiyHN","text_ar":"حَرَاجِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, L.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajapN","text_ar":"حَرَجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places.       -A4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing composed of pieces of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bound together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which dead bodies are carried;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes put over the bier of a woman:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) accord. to the T, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hrj","text_ar":"حرج"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a bier is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ijaAr","text_ar":"شِجَار"},{"kind":"text","text":", [i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frame-work of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawodaj","text_ar":"هَوْدَج"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is constructed of wood, and put over the bier of a corpse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to ISd, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hrj","text_ar":"حرج"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vehicle for women and men, which has no head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEo$N","text_ar":"نَعْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["Yoo","S","K","A","TA","L","As"]},{"entry_id":"n7569","headword_ar":"حَرِجٌ","root":"Hrj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strait, narrow, confined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"close,"},{"kind":"text","text":"place: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strait, narrow, confined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"close, in the utmost degree:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, T:) or a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strait, narrow, confined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"close,"},{"kind":"text","text":"place,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abounding with trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and impenetrable to the pasturing animals:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HariyjN","text_ar":"حَرِيجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, applied to a place, signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarijN","text_ar":"حَرِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SadorN HarijN","text_ar":"صَدْرٌ حَرِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waHidN","text_ar":"وَحِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waHadN","text_ar":"وَحَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faridN","text_ar":"فَرِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faradN","text_ar":"فَرَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"danifN","text_ar":"دَنِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"danafN","text_ar":"دَنَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bosom strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not expanded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dilated, by reason of what is good."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yajoEalo Sadorahu Day~iqFA HarijFA","text_ar":"يَجْعَلْ صَدْرَهُ ضَيِّقًا حَرِجًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajFA","text_ar":"حَرَجًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different readings, [in the Kur vi. 125,] (S,) is explained by I 'Ab as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He will make his bosom strait."},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impenetrable"},{"kind":"text","text":"to wisdom. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarijN","text_ar":"حَرِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a strait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted, bosom, which does not expand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dilate, by reason of what is good:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the former has a dual and a pl.; but the latter has only the sing. form, because it is [properly, or originally,] an inf. n.: Zj says that the former is a part. n., and that by the latter is meant"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw HarajK","text_ar":"ذُو حَرَجٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-  And the former, (assumed tropical:)  One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who fears,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dreads, to venture upon an affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That seldom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"never, withdraws from fight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that will not be put to flight;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were difficult for him to find an excuse for being put to flight. (TA.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Committing a sin, a crime,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an act of disobedience for which he deserves punishment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaArijN","text_ar":"حَارِجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is thought by ISd to be after the manner of a rel. n., because it has no corresponding verb [of which it may be regarded as the part. n.; the regular part. n. being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarijN","text_ar":"حَرِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harija","text_ar":"حَرِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is intrans.]. (TA.) ―         -b7-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Abstaining from sin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crime;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutaHar~ijN","text_ar":"مُتَحَرِّجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [Thus bearing two contr. significations. See 5.] ―         -b8-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Forbidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prohibited:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zulomuka","text_ar":"ظُلْمُكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY~a HarijN","text_ar":"عَلَىَّ حَرِجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarajN","text_ar":"حَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wronging of thee is forbidden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prohibited, to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Zj","T","S","K","Msb","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}